      <data key="d1">Ask Alex mode: interrogating sorted records with AI</data>
      <data key="d2">0.9</data>
      <data key="d3">[{"quote": "the primary mode would be Ask Alex, which is pretty much just an Ask AI, where the user would be able to interrogate the sorted records.", "ts": 956.5, "source": "transcript"}, {"quote": "they'd only be able to interrogate MedWeb sorted records. So in other words, it would have to be sorted records that's within the records parent folder.", "ts": 970.2, "source": "transcript"}]</data>
