      <data key="d2">0.9</data>
      <data key="d3">[{"quote": "usually if the clinician is busy with it, it will be in progress, sorry, allocated. And then once they're done, it still needs to be QA'd. And then so it's ready for QA, then it gets QA'd. And then once QA is done, then it gets uploaded and released.", "ts": 2472.0, "source": "transcript"}]</data>
      <data key="d4">["chapter:09"]</data>
      <data key="d20">The ECA status lifecycle is: allocated (clinician working) → ready for QA → QA'd → uploaded and released.</data>
