      <data key="d1">MedBrief Match has a distinct colour palette to visually differentiate AI features</data>
      <data key="d2">0.9</data>
      <data key="d3">[{"quote": "you can see also the color palette for this is very different compared to the rest of the product. So we, yeah, so this was specific for expert match.", "ts": 3107.1, "source": "transcript"}, {"quote": "we're also going to be applying the same color to MedBreat Insights. Not as much though, not as drastic as what we're doing here, but at least for the button to stand out, as well as the logo that we're using, just bringing a little bit of the purple as well, because we want to tie in all the AI type peaches with this particular color palette.", "ts": 3117.9, "source": "transcript"}]</data>
      <data key="d4">["chapter:11"]</data>
      <data key="d20">MedBrief Match uses a distinct purple-dominated colour palette, different from the rest of the product, to visually group all AI-type features. The same palette will be applied more subtly to MedBrief Insights.</data>
