    <node id="claim:0051">
      <data key="d0">Claim</data>
      <data key="d1">MedBrief Match uses similar-case cross-referencing across all Match matters, but only shows client-specific case details</data>
      <data key="d2">0.9</data>
      <data key="d3">[{"quote": "we take the information on the matter and then we cross-reference that with the matters that are really on MedBreatMatch to see which other matters has experts worked on that's similar to this particular matters information.", "ts": 3219.6, "source": "transcript"}, {"quote": "while we are able to show the total count of similar cases that the expert has worked on across MedBreatMatch, we can only show them the details of line matters, of the client's matters for obvious reasons.", "ts": 3278.3, "source": "transcript"}]</data>
      <data key="d4">["chapter:12"]</data>
      <data key="d20">MedBrief Match cross-references a matter against all Match matters to find similar cases; it shows the total similar-case count across the platform but restricts case detail to the current client's own matters.</data>
