    <node id="claim:0052">
      <data key="d0">Claim</data>
      <data key="d1">Expert hourly rates and turnaround times in profiles are initially absent (AI-sourced profiles lack this); data is populated after expert contact</data>
      <data key="d2">0.9</data>
      <data key="d3">[{"quote": "Most of these don't have this information yet because we, like I said, we generated the expert's profile information from the internet. We don't have this information what the hourly rate is or the average turnaround time.", "ts": 3302.2, "source": "transcript"}, {"quote": "This one is an expert that's already been contacted via MedBreatMatch. So he obviously completed his hourly rate and his turnaround time.", "ts": 3313.3, "source": "transcript"}]</data>
      <data key="d4">["chapter:12"]</data>
