      <data key="d3">[{"quote": "we just give the reasons as to why this particular expert was recommended. And we do that for every single expert.", "ts": 3470.2, "source": "transcript"}]</data>
      <data key="d4">["chapter:12"]</data>
      <data key="d20">For every expert returned in a MedBrief Match search, the platform AI-generates a set of recommendation reasons explaining why that expert is suited to the matter.</data>
