      <data key="d2">0.9</data>
      <data key="d3">[{"quote": "At the moment, the standard template will be used for all clients. But somewhere along the future, we will have functionality where the client can customize it.", "ts": 3509, "source": "transcript"}, {"quote": "So it will probably not be a UI thing where they can customize it themselves. They will need to let us know what they wanted to customize it as. And then we'll add a client-specific template.", "ts": 3517, "source": "transcript"}]</data>
      <data key="d4">["chapter:13"]</data>
