      <data key="d0">Claim</data>
      <data key="d1">Sufficient-information criteria: background + key events above minimum character count, OR an ECA, chronology, or clinical summary</data>
      <data key="d2">0.95</data>
      <data key="d3">[{"quote": "the criteria for that is, is that a matter, you know, the, when we complete in the matter creation, whether it asks you for the background and as well as the key events. So that needs to be above a certain, a minimum character count.", "ts": 3669, "source": "transcript"}, {"quote": "Either that, or it needs an early case assessment or a chronology or a clinical summary or act.", "ts": 3682, "source": "transcript"}]</data>
      <data key="d4">["chapter:13"]</data>
      <data key="d20">A matter qualifies for MedBrief Match if: (a) background + key events fields exceed a minimum character count, OR (b) the matter has an early case assessment, chronology, or clinical summary.</data>
