    <node id="decision:0009">
      <data key="d0">Decision</data>
      <data key="d1">Display total similar-case count across all Match matters, but restrict case details to the client's own matters</data>
      <data key="d2">0.9</data>
      <data key="d3">[{"quote": "we are going to be changing it that we display the total number of cases regardless of the clients. But then when you view the profile, you'll see in a moment when the client views the profile, we actually show them the details of that similar case. So while we are able to show the total count of similar cases that the expert has worked on across MedBreatMatch, we can only show them the details of line matters, of the client's matters for obvious reasons.", "ts": 3263.3, "source": "transcript"}]</data>
      <data key="d4">["chapter:12"]</data>
      <data key="d20">MedBrief Match will display the total number of similar cases an expert has worked on across the whole platform, but restrict the detailed case view to the current client's own matters.</data>
