    <node id="decision:0011">
      <data key="d0">Decision</data>
      <data key="d1">T&amp;Cs required from expert for any response (accept, decline, or request more info) despite drop-off risk</data>
      <data key="d2">0.9</data>
      <data key="d3">[{"quote": "whether they decline, accept, or they request any more information for them to, to be able to continue, they have to, to have to agree to the terms and conditions", "ts": 4371, "source": "transcript"}, {"quote": "We are trying this and just see, um, hopefully there won't be too much of a drop off.", "ts": 4389, "source": "transcript"}]</data>
      <data key="d4">["chapter:14"]</data>
      <data key="d20">The decision was made to require experts to accept MedBrief terms and conditions regardless of their response type (accept, decline or request info), even though this carries a drop-off risk for declining experts.</data>
