      <data key="d47">The admin manage section covering clients, firms (API import via Kennedys), matters, users and incomplete matters, plus DocSorter configuration such as clinical sections, sorting instructions and file-note phrases. Also covers expert agencies, records request centres, service options and timelines, billing items including the MedBrief Match markup, and generating invoices that sync to Xero.</data>
