      <data key="d0">VisualContext</data>
      <data key="d1">MedBrief Match - welcome / intro modal</data>
      <data key="d2">0.9</data>
      <data key="d3">[{"quote": "Welcome to MedBrief Match. MedBrief Match connects you with the most relevant medical experts for your case. Expert search: find the right medical expert with the help of MedBrief, designed to accelerate and improve confidence when building your expert panel. Automated Letters of Approach: quickly generate your Letter of Approach with AI-assisted case summaries, editing, drafting and sending - all from within. Intelligent similar case matching: leverage AI-powered analysis of similar cases and expert specialities to receive tailored recommendations. Seamless expert communication: manage all expert communications. [Don't show this again] [Close]. Matter: Mr Darren Joseph -v- United Lincolnshire Hospitals NHS Trust. Tabs: Matter dashboard, Records, Radiology, Users, Disclosures, Communications, Download.", "ts": 2854.125, "source": "vision"}]</data>
      <data key="d4">["chapter:11"]</data>
      <data key="d52">frame-00045.png</data>
      <data key="d53">2854.125</data>
      <data key="d54">app</data>
      <data key="d55">Welcome to MedBrief Match. MedBrief Match connects you with the most relevant medical experts for your case. Expert search: find the right medical expert with the help of MedBrief, designed to accelerate and improve confidence when building your expert panel. Automated Letters of Approach: quickly generate your Letter of Approach with AI-assisted case summaries, editing, drafting and sending - all from within. Intelligent similar case matching: leverage AI-powered analysis of similar cases and expert specialities to receive tailored recommendations. Seamless expert communication: manage all expert communications. [Don't show this again] [Close]. Matter: Mr Darren Joseph -v- United Lincolnshire Hospitals NHS Trust. Tabs: Matter dashboard, Records, Radiology, Users, Disclosures, Communications, Download.</data>
      <data key="d31">The MedBrief Match feature opens with a welcome modal inside the Darren Joseph matter, explaining how it connects a case with relevant medical experts. It frames the four pillars of the expert-matching workflow, which matters because Match is the entry point for finding and instructing experts from within the platform.</data>
      <data key="d56">a4bdf0f1f0e0f08c</data>
    </node>
    <node id="visual:0030">
      <data key="d0">VisualContext</data>
      <data key="d1">MedBrief Match - Find the right expert search form</data>
      <data key="d2">0.9</data>
      <data key="d3">[{"quote": "Find the right expert for your case [Beta]. Speciality*: Select expert specialities. Recommended specialities generated by MedBrief: Trauma and Orthopaedics, Physiotherapy, Radiology, General Practice. Consultation element: Select a consultation element. Ask MedBrief Match: describe what type of expert you're looking for; search for keywords or select any one of the recommended queries below. Or select from these recommended searches generated by MedBrief: Looking for a trauma and orthopaedics expert to assess incorrect placement of a shoulder replacement implant and its impact on function; Need an orthopaedic surgeon experienced in revision shoulder arthroplasty to review possible surgical error and ongoing pain; Seeking a radiologist to evaluate imaging for evidence of malpositioned shoulder prosthesis and causation of restricted movement; Require a physiotherapist to comment on rehabilitation and whether ongoing symptoms are consistent with surgical breach; Find a general practice expert to review post-operative management and referral decisions in persistent shoulder pain after replacement. [Search experts]", "ts": 2857.562, "source": "vision"}]</data>
      <data key="d4">["chapter:11"]</data>
      <data key="d52">frame-00046.png</data>
      <data key="d53">2857.562</data>
