      <data key="d55">Find the right expert for your case [Beta]. Speciality*: Select expert specialities. Recommended specialities generated by MedBrief: Trauma and Orthopaedics, Physiotherapy, Radiology, General Practice. Consultation element: Select a consultation element. Ask MedBrief Match: describe what type of expert you're looking for; search for keywords or select any one of the recommended queries below. Or select from these recommended searches generated by MedBrief: Looking for a trauma and orthopaedics expert to assess incorrect placement of a shoulder replacement implant and its impact on function; Need an orthopaedic surgeon experienced in revision shoulder arthroplasty to review possible surgical error and ongoing pain; Seeking a radiologist to evaluate imaging for evidence of malpositioned shoulder prosthesis and causation of restricted movement; Require a physiotherapist to comment on rehabilitation and whether ongoing symptoms are consistent with surgical breach; Find a general practice expert to review post-operative management and referral decisions in persistent shoulder pain after replacement. [Search experts]</data>
      <data key="d31">The Match search form lets the user pick a speciality, accept MedBrief-recommended specialities, set a consultation element, and ask MedBrief Match in natural language or pick a generated suggested search. This shows how Match turns case context into a structured expert query.</data>
