    <node id="visual:0033">
      <data key="d0">VisualContext</data>
      <data key="d1">MedBrief Match - expert profile (Dr Alastair Bint)</data>
      <data key="d2">0.9</data>
      <data key="d3">[{"quote": "Expert profile. Dr Alastair Bint - Freelance GP and General Practice Expert Witness. Guildford. 28 years experience. Caudation [Causation]. [Add to shortlist] [Generate Letter of Approach]. Tabs: Profile details, Similar cases, Case history, Recommendation reasons. Summary: Dr Alastair Bint serves as an NHS GP, bringing more than 28 years of clinical practice, and is currently engaged as a freelance GP as well as Chambers Lead at Pallant Medical Chambers. He possesses substantial experience as a General Practice Expert Witness, having delivered expert opinions in excess of 7,000 alleged medical negligence matters, representing both claimants and defendants. His medico-legal proficiency encompasses involvement in Coronial Inquests, GMC Fitness to Practise proceedings, and both civil and criminal litigation. Career history: 2020-present Freelance GP, Wilton Practice, Alton; 2015-2020 GP and Chambers Lead, Pallant Medical Chambers, Guildford; 2008-2014 Partner, NHS Training General Practice, St Luke's Surgery. Research &amp; publications. Prizes &amp; awards: 2010 Clinical Champion for Integrated Healthcare in Surrey. Areas of expertise. Engagement details.", "ts": 3370.438, "source": "vision"}]</data>
      <data key="d4">["chapter:12"]</data>
      <data key="d52">frame-00050.png</data>
      <data key="d53">3370.438</data>
      <data key="d54">app</data>
      <data key="d55">Expert profile. Dr Alastair Bint - Freelance GP and General Practice Expert Witness. Guildford. 28 years experience. Caudation [Causation]. [Add to shortlist] [Generate Letter of Approach]. Tabs: Profile details, Similar cases, Case history, Recommendation reasons. Summary: Dr Alastair Bint serves as an NHS GP, bringing more than 28 years of clinical practice, and is currently engaged as a freelance GP as well as Chambers Lead at Pallant Medical Chambers. He possesses substantial experience as a General Practice Expert Witness, having delivered expert opinions in excess of 7,000 alleged medical negligence matters, representing both claimants and defendants. His medico-legal proficiency encompasses involvement in Coronial Inquests, GMC Fitness to Practise proceedings, and both civil and criminal litigation. Career history: 2020-present Freelance GP, Wilton Practice, Alton; 2015-2020 GP and Chambers Lead, Pallant Medical Chambers, Guildford; 2008-2014 Partner, NHS Training General Practice, St Luke's Surgery. Research &amp; publications. Prizes &amp; awards: 2010 Clinical Champion for Integrated Healthcare in Surrey. Areas of expertise. Engagement details.</data>
      <data key="d31">An individual expert profile panel for Dr Alastair Bint, showing summary, career history, research and publications, prizes and awards, areas of expertise, engagement details and qualifications. The Generate Letter of Approach and Add to shortlist actions at the top tie expert vetting directly into instructing them.</data>
