      <data key="d2">0.9</data>
      <data key="d3">[{"quote": "Cancel Letter of Approach? You have unsaved changes. Cancelling now will discard all edits made to this letter. Are you sure you want to continue? [Discard changes] [Continue editing]. Behind dialog: Records obtained (Update required); Progress of litigation; Information requested - if you are willing and able to consider this instruction, could you please confirm the following via the link in the email to be sent: the contact rate within your areas of expertise; any potential conflict of interest in accepting this instruction; average turnaround time for preparing a report; anticipated time required for the instruction; hourly rate for medico-legal work; reasonable number of medico-legal reports per year; typical concerns/details with medico-legal instructions; please provide a copy of your medico-legal CV and standard terms of business.", "ts": 3953.5, "source": "vision"}]</data>
