      <data key="d1">MedBrief Match Messages - expert email thread (Prof. Peter Holt)</data>
      <data key="d2">0.9</data>
      <data key="d3">[{"quote": "Kenneth Banks -v- Kingswinford Medical Practice. MedBrief Match &gt; Experts. All experts: Prof. Peter Holt (Consultant Vascular Surgeon), Mr Shane Macsweeney (Consultant Vascular Surgeon), Mr James Scurr (Consultant Vascular &amp; Endovascular Surgeon), Dr Alastair Bint (Freelance GP and General Practice Expert Witness). Thread - Prof. Peter Holt [View profile], 1 attachment. Wioleta Dworak: 'Dear Professor Holt, Thank you for accepting this case. Please find attached a Letter of Instruction in this matter. Kindly confirm your email address to which a link to MedBrief should be sent for access to medical records and enclosures to be granted...' (Wed 22 May, 12:00, 1 attachment). Peter Holt (Tuesday, 20:55): 'Dear Wioleta, I have been responding to your email with mine unaware that you are only using this portal. The emails address is the one you were approached me on and the one I have been emailing you from. Please can you send me the link as I have not received it yet. Best wishes, Pete'. Compose box. [Save as draft] [Send].", "ts": 4636.938, "source": "vision"}]</data>
      <data key="d4">["chapter:15"]</data>
      <data key="d52">frame-00065.png</data>
      <data key="d53">4636.938</data>
      <data key="d54">app</data>
      <data key="d55">Kenneth Banks -v- Kingswinford Medical Practice. MedBrief Match &gt; Experts. All experts: Prof. Peter Holt (Consultant Vascular Surgeon), Mr Shane Macsweeney (Consultant Vascular Surgeon), Mr James Scurr (Consultant Vascular &amp; Endovascular Surgeon), Dr Alastair Bint (Freelance GP and General Practice Expert Witness). Thread - Prof. Peter Holt [View profile], 1 attachment. Wioleta Dworak: 'Dear Professor Holt, Thank you for accepting this case. Please find attached a Letter of Instruction in this matter. Kindly confirm your email address to which a link to MedBrief should be sent for access to medical records and enclosures to be granted...' (Wed 22 May, 12:00, 1 attachment). Peter Holt (Tuesday, 20:55): 'Dear Wioleta, I have been responding to your email with mine unaware that you are only using this portal. The emails address is the one you were approached me on and the one I have been emailing you from. Please can you send me the link as I have not received it yet. Best wishes, Pete'. Compose box. [Save as draft] [Send].</data>
      <data key="d31">The full message thread with Prof. Peter Holt inside MedBrief Match, showing back-and-forth emails about accepting a Letter of Instruction and confirming the email address to grant the expert access to medical records and enclosures. This is the two-way expert communication channel that keeps instruction correspondence inside the platform.</data>
      <data key="d56">b4b49484948494b0</data>
    </node>
